AI-powered CLI tool for automatically translating AWS Workshop documents.

## Key Features

- ğŸ¤– **AI-Powered Translation**: High-quality translation using Claude models (Opus/Sonnet/Haiku)
- ğŸ“š **AWS Documentation Integration**: Accurate terminology via MCP integration with official AWS docs
- âš¡ **Parallel Processing**: Process up to 5 files simultaneously with ThreadPoolExecutor
- ğŸ”„ **Session Resume**: Continue interrupted work from where you left off
- ğŸ“Š **Quality Management**: 3-stage workflow: Translation â†’ Review â†’ Validation
- ğŸ‘€ **Local Preview**: Instantly preview translation results

## Architecture

Uses an **Orchestrator-centric architecture**.

```
